        Create table with specified database, table name, table description and schema
        Parameters:
        databaseName - Database Name
        tableName - Table Name
        schema - Schema of the new table, if not specified, will use the schema specified in crtTbl
        allowExisting - if true, ignore AlreadyExistsException
        desc - CreateTableDesc object which contains the SerDe info. Currently we support most of the features except the bucket.
